This topic describes how to configure Ops Manager to deploy Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) on Amazon Web Services (AWS).

Before beginning this procedure, ensure that you have successfully completed all of the steps in the [Manually Configuring AWS for PCF](pcf-aws-manual-config.html) topic. After completing the procedures in this topic, proceed to the [Manually Configuring PAS for AWS](pcf-aws-manual-er-config.html) topic to continue deploying PCF.

